<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 06:17:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着中欧紧张局势加剧，Polestar可能利用美国工厂向欧洲销售汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/polestar-may-use-us-plant-sell-cars-europe-eu-china-tension-rises-2024-04-24/</link><description>中国支持的瑞典电动汽车 (EV) 制造商 Polestar Automotive 首席执行官表示，鉴于地缘政治紧张局势加剧，该公司正准备将其计划销往欧洲的汽车生产从中国转移到美国工厂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 06:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/polestar-may-use-us-plant-sell-cars-europe-eu-china-tension-rises-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>彭博新闻报道，中国碧桂园延长债券期限以避免首次本地违约</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-country-garden-extends-bonds-avoid-first-local-default-bloomberg-news-2024-04-24/</link><description>彭博社周三援引知情人士的话报道称，中国开发商碧桂园控股公司已获准推迟支付三种人民币债券。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:57:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-country-garden-extends-bonds-avoid-first-local-default-bloomberg-news-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国的电动汽车生存游戏带来危险和力量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ev-survival-game-creates-peril-power-2024-04-24/</link><description>从大多数标准来看，中国最不需要的就是更多的电动汽车挤入一个输家多于赢家的市场，以牺牲利润为代价压低价格，并争夺中国以外的市场份额。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ev-survival-game-creates-peril-power-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国寻求对币安创始人赵判处 36 个月监禁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-seeks-36-months-jail-binance-founder-zhao-2024-04-24/</link><description>美国检察官周二在一份法庭文件中表示，全球最大的加密货币交易所币安创始人赵长鹏在承认违反反洗钱法后，应入狱 36 个月。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:44:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-seeks-36-months-jail-binance-founder-zhao-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>Orsted表示，为台积电提供电力的台湾风电项目有望于2025年完成</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/orsted-says-taiwan-wind-project-power-tsmc-track-2025-finish-2024-04-24/</link><description>全球最大的海上风电场开发商丹麦Orsted周三表示，台湾的一个项目将为芯片制造商台积电提供电力，进展顺利，有望于明年完工。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:26:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/orsted-says-taiwan-wind-project-power-tsmc-track-2025-finish-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>随着成本下降，沃尔沃汽车第一季度调整后营业利润上升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-q1-adjusted-operating-earnings-rise-costs-ease-2024-04-24/</link><description>瑞典汽车制造商沃尔沃汽车周三报告称，得益于材料成本下降和销量增加，第一季度调整后营业利润有所增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:08:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-q1-adjusted-operating-earnings-rise-costs-ease-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯开始访华后，美中关系有所改善，但分歧仍很严重</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/better-us-china-ties-still-deep-disagreements-blinken-starts-visit-2024-04-24/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周三抵达上海，美中关系基础更加稳定，但一系列令人畏惧的悬而未决的问题威胁着全球竞争对手之间关系的稳定。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:04:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/better-us-china-ties-still-deep-disagreements-blinken-starts-visit-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对中国医疗器械市场启动调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-opens-investigation-into-chinese-medical-device-market-2024-04-24/</link><description>欧盟官方公报周三称，欧盟委员会周三对中国公共采购医疗器械展开调查，以确定欧洲供应商是否获得公平准入。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-opens-investigation-into-chinese-medical-device-market-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国华为推出新的智能驾驶软件品牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-huawei-launches-new-software-intelligent-driving-2024-04-24/</link><description>中国科技公司华为（HWT.UL）周三推出了新的智能驾驶软件品牌，标志着其为成为电动汽车行业主要参与者而做出的最新努力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 03:57:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-huawei-launches-new-software-intelligent-driving-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因科技股上涨而上涨；干预观察中日元脆弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-24/</link><description>周三，亚洲股市在科技股的带动下大幅上涨，投资者本周将注意力转向美国科技领头羊的财报，而日元仍深陷 34 年来的低点附近，令交易员对日本当局的干预保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 03:06:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国华为推出智能驾驶新品牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-huawei-launches-new-brand-intelligent-driving-2024-04-24/</link><description>中国科技巨头华为（HWT.UL）周三推出了智能驾驶新品牌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 02:41:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-huawei-launches-new-brand-intelligent-driving-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉在中国推出 Model 3、Model Y 零首付</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-offers-zero-down-payments-model-3-model-y-china-2024-04-24/</link><description>特斯拉社交媒体账户上的一则通知显示，特斯拉公司已为其在中国的 Model 3 和 Model Y 车辆提供零首付。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 02:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-offers-zero-down-payments-model-3-model-y-china-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>解说员：美国 TikTok 法案已通过，现在会发生什么？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/what-happens-now-that-us-tiktok-bill-has-been-passed-2024-04-24/</link><description>美国参议院周二通过立法，给予 TikTok 的中国所有者字节跳动大约九个月的时间剥离该短视频应用程序的美国资产，否则将面临全国范围的禁令。总统乔·拜登表示，他将于周三将该法案签署成为法律。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 02:12:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/what-happens-now-that-us-tiktok-bill-has-been-passed-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛的索加瓦雷表示，他在新政府的紧张等待中负责安全工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-sogavare-says-he-runs-security-amid-tense-wait-new-government-2024-04-24/</link><description>所罗门群岛总理马内塞·索加瓦雷表示，他以微弱优势赢得了席位，并且仍在这个太平洋岛国行使安全权力，在选举没有明显获胜者后，他正在与反对党争夺组建政府。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 01:39:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-sogavare-says-he-runs-security-amid-tense-wait-new-government-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院有足够票数通过乌克兰、以色列援助法案，投票仍在继续</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-senate-has-enough-votes-pass-ukraine-israel-aid-bill-voting-continues-2024-04-24/</link><description>美国参议院周二支持一项价值 950 亿美元的对外援助计划，为乌克兰、以色列和台湾提供安全援助，并获得足够票数将该措施提交白宫供总统拜登签署成为法律。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 01:31:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-senate-has-enough-votes-pass-ukraine-israel-aid-bill-voting-continues-2024-04-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>